  <brief_title>Susceptibility to High Altitude Pulmonary Edema in Subjects With Increased Hypoxic Pulmonary Vasoconstriction</brief_title>
  <official_title>Susceptibility to High Altitude Pulmonary Edema in Subjects With Increased Pulmonary Artery Pressure During Exercise in Normoxia and at Rest in Hypoxia</official_title>
