  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  abnormal increase of pulmonary artery pressure at rest in hypoxia and during exercise
             in normoxia

          -  ability to climb Margherita Hut

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Birth at or above 1500 m altitude

          -  any cardiovascular or pulmonary disease

          -  Infection disease

          -  Intake of drugs, in particular Acetazolamide, Nifedipine, corticosteroids or
             PDE-5-inhibitors.

          -  Pregnancy
      </textblock>
